# Build outputs, caches, and machine-specific config under the vendored app/.
# The vendored Kai source's origin commit is recorded
# in VENDOR.txt. Standard (unanchored) patterns so they match at any depth.
#
# NOTE: scripts/committer uses `git add --force`, which bypasses these rules —
# clean build dirs (./gradlew clean) before committing the app/ directory, or
# commit specific files.
.gradle/
.kotlin/
build/
local.properties
captures/
.cxx/
/.vendor.*
*.apk
*.aab
